[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.42.0"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread", "fs", "process", "signal"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]

features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.11.0"
features = ["v4"]
